===Noun===
{{en-noun|-|s}}

# The [[belief]] that proposes the [[absence]] and [[abolition]] of [[hierarchy]] and [[authority]] in most [[form]]s.
## {{lb|en|specifically}} A [[political]] and [[philosophical]] belief that all forms of [[involuntary]] [[rule]] or government are [[undesirable]], [[unnecessary]], or [[unethical]], and that [[society]] could [[function]] without a ruler or involuntary government (a [[state]]).

